            "value": "<p><em>Speaking an incantation in a forgotten language, you conjure</em> <em>a winding red and black beam of enervating energy, which springs from your finger toward your target.</em></p><p><strong>Constitution Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[Weakened]. Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting</strong>: <span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">Target one additional creature for each spell level above 2nd.</span></p>",
